Give a warm welcome to our newest member ${mentionedUser}!

*Information about the server can be found in* #information *, server rules can be found in* #rules *,and you can assign yourself some identity roles in* #change-roles .

Have a wonderful time here!
If you ever need some help, feel free to message one of our Peacekeepers.

actions.message: Queer Club is a discord server providing a safe and positive space for LGBTQ+ community members to chat, make friends, and get support.
actions.name: Set Embed Description

actions.message:
To report a member, you can use our report bot command.
```.report @user {reason}```
Replace `{reason}` with the reason for your report (including the `{}`'s)

actions.message:
Administrator (Admin) is the highest staff rank.
Admins have all permissions and are the part of the management team.
actions.name: Add Embed Field

actions.message:
Lead Peacekeepers are the top dogs of the Peacekeeping team.
Holding all moderation powers, they keep the peacekeepers in check and help moderate the chat.
They're part of the management team.
actions.name: Add Embed Field

actions.message: Peacekeepers, otherwise are our servers moderators. They're responsible for keeping the peace by upholding the server rules and dealing punishment where necessary.
actions.name: Add Embed Field

actions.message:
Assistants are our lowest ranked staff members.
They're here to help answer your questions and guide you to the right staff member if you're in need of more help.
